# AI-Powered Project Management Platform

## Overview

This document outlines the requirements for an AI-powered project management platform that uses machine learning to optimize team productivity, predict project risks, and automate routine management tasks. The platform will integrate with existing tools and provide intelligent insights to help teams deliver projects on time and within budget.

## Goals and Objectives

- **Primary Goal**: Create an intelligent project management system that reduces management overhead by 70%
- **Objective 1**: Automate task assignment based on team member skills and availability
- **Objective 2**: Predict project risks and timeline delays with 90% accuracy
- **Objective 3**: Provide real-time insights and recommendations for project optimization
- **Success Criteria**: 50% reduction in project delays, 80% user satisfaction, 40% improvement in team productivity

## Functional Requirements

### Feature 1: Intelligent Task Management
- **Must have**: AI-powered task creation from natural language descriptions
- **Must have**: Automatic task prioritization based on dependencies and deadlines
- **Must have**: Smart task assignment considering team member skills, workload, and availability
- **Should have**: Task effort estimation using historical data and ML models
- **Nice to have**: Voice-based task creation and updates

### Feature 2: Predictive Analytics Dashboard
- **Critical**: Real-time project health monitoring with risk indicators
- **Critical**: Timeline prediction with confidence intervals
- **Must have**: Budget burn rate analysis and forecasting
- **Should have**: Team performance metrics and optimization suggestions
- **Nice to have**: Customizable AI-generated reports

### Feature 3: Team Collaboration Hub
- **Essential**: Real-time messaging with context-aware AI assistance
- **Must have**: Automated meeting scheduling based on team availability
- **Must have**: AI-generated meeting summaries and action items
- **Should have**: Sentiment analysis for team communication
- **Could have**: Virtual AI project assistant

### Feature 4: Integration Framework
- **Critical**: REST API for third-party integrations
- **Must have**: GitHub/GitLab integration for development tracking
- **Must have**: Slack/Teams integration for notifications
- **Should have**: Jira/Asana data import and sync
- **Nice to have**: Custom webhook support

## Technical Requirements

- **Architecture**: Microservices architecture with event-driven communication
- **Frontend**: React with TypeScript, responsive design for mobile/desktop
- **Backend**: Node.js with Express, GraphQL API
- **Database**: PostgreSQL for structured data, Redis for caching
- **AI/ML**: Python services with TensorFlow/PyTorch for ML models
- **Infrastructure**: Kubernetes deployment on AWS with auto-scaling
- **Security**: JWT authentication, end-to-end encryption, RBAC

## Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance
- Page load time < 2 seconds
- API response time < 200ms for 95% of requests
- Support 10,000 concurrent users
- 99.9% uptime SLA

### Security
- SOC 2 Type II compliance
- GDPR compliant data handling
- Regular security audits
- Encrypted data at rest and in transit

### Scalability
- Horizontal scaling for all services
- Database sharding for large datasets
- CDN for global content delivery
- Message queue for async processing

## Constraints

- **Timeline**: MVP must be delivered within 6 months
- **Budget**: Total development budget of $500,000
- **Team**: Maximum team size of 15 developers
- **Regulatory**: Must comply with GDPR and CCPA
- **Technical**: Must support IE11 for enterprise clients

## User Stories

### As a Project Manager
- I want to create projects using natural language so that I can quickly set up new initiatives
- I want to see AI-predicted risks so that I can take preventive actions
- I want automated status reports so that I spend less time on administrative tasks

### As a Developer
- I want to receive tasks that match my skills so that I can work efficiently
- I want realistic time estimates so that I can plan my work better
- I want integration with my development tools so that updates are automatic

### As an Executive
- I want real-time project dashboards so that I can monitor portfolio health
- I want predictive analytics so that I can make informed decisions
- I want automated insights so that I can identify optimization opportunities

## Acceptance Criteria

- All API endpoints return responses within 200ms
- ML models achieve >85% accuracy in predictions
- System handles 10,000 concurrent users without degradation
- All security requirements pass third-party audit
- User satisfaction score >4.5/5 in beta testing
- Zero critical bugs in production
- 100% test coverage for core functionality